1030
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] Tako i Njemačka.

1031
00:31:01,519 --> 00:31:04,700
[SPEAKER_01] Isto, ona sa ovih svojih milijon imigranata

1032
00:31:04,700 --> 00:31:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] uzme najbolje,

1033
00:31:06,039 --> 00:31:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] a nama će ići i ono drugo.

1034
00:31:07,579 --> 00:31:09,019
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to će biti ljudi

1035
00:31:09,019 --> 00:31:11,160
[SPEAKER_01] koji će biti isključivo na socijalnoj pomoći,

1036
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,140
[SPEAKER_01] zato ja kažem,

1037
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:15,559
[SPEAKER_01] bolje plati 20.000 eura po glavi,

1038
00:31:15,559 --> 00:31:17,279
[SPEAKER_01] manje će nas koštati

1039
00:31:17,279 --> 00:31:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] nego da uzimamo socijalne slučajeve

1040
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] iz Afrike i Bliskog Istoka.

1041
00:31:22,119 --> 00:31:24,160
[SPEAKER_00] A što ako nam prodaju priču,

1042
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:26,299
[SPEAKER_00] pa evo, nema naših ljudi,

1043
00:31:26,299 --> 00:31:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] nema ko bi radio,

1044
00:31:27,579 --> 00:31:28,859
[SPEAKER_00] pa i ovo je dobro došlo.

1045
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:31,279
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, na žalost, upravo to čitamo svaki dan

1046
00:31:31,279 --> 00:31:34,259
[SPEAKER_01] u tim globalističkim medijima,

1047
00:31:34,259 --> 00:31:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] većinom u vlasništvu Srbije.

1048
00:31:37,079 --> 00:31:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] Čitamo da, eto,

1049
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] oni rade poslove koje mi ne bi željeli.

1050
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] Molim, koliko se ja sjećam,

1051
00:31:45,380 --> 00:31:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] do prije koje godine,

1052
00:31:47,019 --> 00:31:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] svi dostavljači hrane u Hrvatskoj

1053
00:31:49,920 --> 00:31:51,759
[SPEAKER_01] su bili hrvatski kađer.

1054
00:31:51,759 --> 00:31:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] Susjedi i tako dalje.

1055
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,880
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje su nestali?

1056
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,599
[SPEAKER_01] Kakve su to laži i gluposti?

1057
00:31:56,599 --> 00:31:58,240
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nisu nestali,

1058
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,619
[SPEAKER_01] nego ove možeš platiti

1059
00:31:59,619 --> 00:32:00,920
[SPEAKER_01] nikoliko on opet sretan.

1060
00:32:00,920 --> 00:32:02,680
[SPEAKER_01] Njih tisuću nakrcaš,

1061
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] ono, uše,

1062
00:32:03,720 --> 00:32:04,819
[SPEAKER_01] nije kreveti na kat,

1063
00:32:04,819 --> 00:32:06,859
[SPEAKER_01] nego sad su kreveti nebuderi

1064
00:32:06,859 --> 00:32:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] u jednoj sobi.

1065
00:32:07,539 --> 00:32:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, gdje spavaju kosardinice,

1066
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,359
[SPEAKER_01] ono, 30 centimetara ima

1067
00:32:11,359 --> 00:32:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] prostor za vuce i to je to.

1068
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,279
[SPEAKER_01] I ljudi rade ono jer dolaze

1069
00:32:15,279 --> 00:32:16,680
[SPEAKER_01] iz još siromašnijih država

1070
00:32:16,680 --> 00:32:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] i taj novac njima znači.

1071
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je put u nestanak

1072
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] mirovinskog fonda.

1073
00:32:20,539 --> 00:32:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] To je put, znači,

1074
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,200
[SPEAKER_01] nema mirovina.

1075
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,839
[SPEAKER_01] Mi već sada nemamo

1076
00:32:23,839 --> 00:32:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] za isplatu 50% mirovina.

1077
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] A sad zamislite još

1078
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:28,900
[SPEAKER_01] sa tom količinom

1079
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,660
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi koji rade za još manje.

1080
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će onda uopće

1081
00:32:31,940 --> 00:32:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskoj ostati od Hrvata?

1082
00:32:33,579 --> 00:32:35,779
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, zamjena stanovništva

1083
00:32:35,779 --> 00:32:37,440
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskoj je moguća

1084
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,859
[SPEAKER_01] za doslovce 3 mjeseca.

1085
00:32:38,859 --> 00:32:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] Doslovce 3 mjeseca.

1086
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:43,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vi imate, mi već sada imamo

1087
00:32:43,119 --> 00:32:45,480
[SPEAKER_01] 300 tisuća stranih radnika.

1088
00:32:45,480 --> 00:32:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Malo samo izmijenite

1089
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] zakonodavstvo kao što je

1090
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:50,240
[SPEAKER_01] izmijenjeno u Francuskoj.

1091
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači što je Macron

1092
00:32:51,119 --> 00:32:53,339
[SPEAKER_01] savršeno izveo prevarom

1093
00:32:53,339 --> 00:32:54,339
[SPEAKER_01] Marine Le Pen.

1094
00:32:54,339 --> 00:32:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] I, znači, imate 300 tisuća.

1095
00:32:57,859 --> 00:32:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] Njima dozvolite, znači,

1096
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] dovođenje obitelji,

1097
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] sjecanje državljanstva

1098
00:33:02,460 --> 00:33:03,240
[SPEAKER_01] i oni imaju pobidu

1099
00:33:03,240 --> 00:33:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] na izborima za 3 mjeseca.

1100
00:33:04,599 --> 00:33:05,160
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ih milijuni.

1101
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:07,240
[SPEAKER_01] Znači 300, znači pročna obitelj je

1102
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] vani pet, u Hrvatskoj je 2 ili 1.

1103
00:33:10,940 --> 00:33:11,680
[SPEAKER_01] Plus pas.

1104
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:13,720
[SPEAKER_01] Plus pas, barim 1.

1105
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:14,759
[SPEAKER_01] Da, barim 1.

1106
00:33:14,759 --> 00:33:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, kod nas je dovedeno,

1107
00:33:18,019 --> 00:33:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] znači Hrvatska ima 60%

1108
00:33:20,079 --> 00:33:21,079
[SPEAKER_01] kućnih ljubimaca.

1109
00:33:21,079 --> 00:33:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kućni ljubimci su uvijek

1110
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] bili dopuna obitelji,

1111
00:33:24,940 --> 00:33:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] a sada kućni ljubimci

1112
00:33:26,420 --> 00:33:28,279
[SPEAKER_01] postaju zamjene obitelji.

1113
00:33:28,279 --> 00:33:30,059
[SPEAKER_00] Jel vas to sablažnjava?

1114
00:33:30,059 --> 00:33:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mene da.

1115
00:33:31,660 --> 00:33:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] svakog normalne.

1116
00:33:32,400 --> 00:33:33,359
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što, znači,

1117
00:33:33,359 --> 00:33:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] lijepa je ljubav od bilo koje životinje.

1118
00:33:36,319 --> 00:33:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] To je ona jednostavna ljubav.

1119
00:33:37,579 --> 00:33:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] Da, pa svi imamo naše male.

1120
00:33:38,460 --> 00:33:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] Maha ne repom i to.

1121
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ljudsko biće ne može

1122
00:33:42,099 --> 00:33:43,759
[SPEAKER_01] zadovoljiti svoju potrebu

1123
00:33:43,759 --> 00:33:44,740
[SPEAKER_01] za socijalnim,

1124
00:33:44,740 --> 00:33:46,700
[SPEAKER_01] angažmanom i interakcijom

1125
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:48,400
[SPEAKER_01] bez drugih ljudi.

1126
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,359
[SPEAKER_01] To nas je i dovilo

1127
00:33:49,359 --> 00:33:50,779
[SPEAKER_01] do ovog standarda koji imamo.

1128
00:33:50,779 --> 00:33:52,420
[SPEAKER_00] Gospodine Kolakušiću,

1129
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:54,980
[SPEAKER_00] ta naša država propada

1130
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] na svim razinama.

1131
00:33:55,960 --> 00:33:56,700
[SPEAKER_00] Sad će neko reći,

1132
00:33:56,700 --> 00:33:57,279
[SPEAKER_00] joj, pa ne,

1133
00:33:57,279 --> 00:33:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] ti mi smo,

1134
00:33:57,779 --> 00:33:59,720
[SPEAKER_00] pobjedili smo Srbiju u ratu.

1135
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1136
00:34:00,059 --> 00:34:01,259
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1137
00:34:01,259 --> 00:34:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo.

1138
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, jesmo.

1139
00:34:03,039 --> 00:34:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] Da, jesmo, ali danas je 2024.

1140
00:34:04,579 --> 00:34:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] A di su novci?

1141
00:34:04,940 --> 00:34:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, di su nam novci.

1142
00:34:06,759 --> 00:34:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ta Srbija bi uskoro trebala,

1143
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] bi trebala u EU.

1144
00:34:10,599 --> 00:34:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] E, onda bi Hrvatska trebala

1145
00:34:13,460 --> 00:34:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] odlučivati isto tako o tome

1146
00:34:15,380 --> 00:34:18,139
[SPEAKER_00] i postati na neki način

1147
00:34:18,139 --> 00:34:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] kao da postanemo dobri susjedi.

1148
00:34:19,699 --> 00:34:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zapravo vi tu vidite

1149
00:34:21,119 --> 00:34:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] jedan priličan problem.

1150
00:34:22,579 --> 00:34:25,039
[SPEAKER_00] A referiram se na ukidenje jednoglasnosti.

1151
00:34:25,039 --> 00:34:25,400
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1152
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ono jednoglasnost

1153
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:28,099
[SPEAKER_01] koju oni govore kao

1154
00:34:28,099 --> 00:34:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] Orban, Crna, Ovca,

1155
00:34:29,679 --> 00:34:31,639
[SPEAKER_01] moramo sve obuke donositi.

1156
00:34:31,639 --> 00:34:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo što to na jednom primjeru

1157
00:34:33,619 --> 00:34:35,219
[SPEAKER_01] odnosa Hrvatske i Srbije znači.

1158
00:34:35,219 --> 00:34:36,440
[SPEAKER_01] Znamo kako je išlo

1159
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] kada smo mi ulazili u EU.

1160
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] Slovenija je zahtjevala rješenje

1161
00:34:40,239 --> 00:34:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] piranskog zaljeva i tako daj.

1162
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, Srbija je napala

1163
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:45,780
[SPEAKER_01] Republiku Hrvatsku.

1164
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, vojnici Srbije su ratovali

1165
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:50,179
[SPEAKER_01] na teritoriju Hrvatske države.

1166
00:34:50,179 --> 00:34:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] Napravili su ogromnu štetu.

1167
00:34:52,619 --> 00:34:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ubili su skoro 20.000 ljudi.

1168
00:34:56,099 --> 00:34:58,219
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi imamo pravo

1169
00:34:58,219 --> 00:34:59,260
[SPEAKER_01] na ratnu očtetu.

1170
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što su imale

1171
00:35:00,699 --> 00:35:02,320
[SPEAKER_01] i u drugom svjetskom ratu

1172
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:03,440
[SPEAKER_01] sve države od Njemačke.

1173
00:35:03,579 --> 00:35:04,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako i mi imamo pravo

1174
00:35:04,679 --> 00:35:05,599
[SPEAKER_01] na ratnu očtetu

1175
00:35:05,599 --> 00:35:06,900
[SPEAKER_01] od Srbije.

1176
00:35:06,900 --> 00:35:08,860
[SPEAKER_01] Kad imate,

1177
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] kad zadržimo princip jednoglasnosti,

1178
00:35:11,699 --> 00:35:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] onda Hrvatska kaže

1179
00:35:12,619 --> 00:35:14,099
[SPEAKER_01] ne može dok nam ne isplate

1180
00:35:14,099 --> 00:35:14,880
[SPEAKER_01] ratnu očtetu.

1181
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] Stavite to

1182
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,800
[SPEAKER_01] u napregorački stol.

1183
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:20,800
[SPEAKER_01] Kada se ukine jednoglasnost,

1184
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] ne samo da mi možemo

1185
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] lajat na mjesec,

1186
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,619
[SPEAKER_01] nego ćemo i lajat na mjesec.

1187
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ništa od zahtjeva

1188
00:35:27,599 --> 00:35:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] za ratnom oštetom

1189
00:35:29,619 --> 00:35:30,559
[SPEAKER_01] dok postojimo.

1190
00:35:30,559 --> 00:35:31,739
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo,

1191
00:35:31,739 --> 00:35:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] pošto je Hrvatska

1192
00:35:33,380 --> 00:35:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] već 10 godina dobiva

1193
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:36,400
[SPEAKER_01] iz evropskih fonda

1194
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:37,900
[SPEAKER_01] više nego što uplačuje,

1195
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] to razdoblje uskoro ide kraju.

1196
00:35:41,119 --> 00:35:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] Sada, oni koji će biti,

1197
00:35:44,159 --> 00:35:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji nam se pridružaju

1198
00:35:45,059 --> 00:35:46,599
[SPEAKER_01] u EU će dobivat više.

1199
00:35:46,599 --> 00:35:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Srbija, Bosna i Hercegovina, Crna Gora.

1200
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] A mi ćemo Hrvati

1201
00:35:50,500 --> 00:35:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] i hrvatski građani dobijat manje.

1202
00:35:52,380 --> 00:35:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mi ćemo već

1203
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:55,219
[SPEAKER_01] kad Srbija uđe

1204
00:35:55,219 --> 00:35:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] financirati,

1205
00:35:56,579 --> 00:35:58,840
[SPEAKER_01] direktno financirati

1206
00:35:58,840 --> 00:36:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] razvoj, gospodarski razvoj Srbije.

1207
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] I opet ništa o tome ne znamo,

1208
00:36:02,980 --> 00:36:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] niko o tome ništa ne govori.

1209
00:36:03,679 --> 00:36:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] Niko o tome ne priča

1210
00:36:05,139 --> 00:36:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

1211
00:36:05,940 --> 00:36:08,920
[SPEAKER_00] Da, zvuči, zapravo,

1212
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,719
[SPEAKER_00] zvuči vrlo, rekla bih,

1213
00:36:10,719 --> 00:36:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] negativistički, depresivno.

1214
00:36:13,539 --> 00:36:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] To su činjenice.

1215
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] A mi sad idemo građani,

1216
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] smo tu, imamo izbori.

1217
00:36:17,000 --> 00:36:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo, ajmo, e da,

1218
00:36:18,159 --> 00:36:19,760
[SPEAKER_00] što očekujete od tih izbora?

1219
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, izbori mogli smo imati...

1220
00:36:21,900 --> 00:36:22,820
[SPEAKER_00] Govorimo o EU izborima,

1221
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] od ovih više nemamo očekivati.

1222
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, EU izbori imali smo

1223
00:36:26,659 --> 00:36:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] opriliku, govorio sam to

1224
00:36:28,059 --> 00:36:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] nekoliko puta,

1225
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] da se te suverenističke

1226
00:36:31,360 --> 00:36:32,900
[SPEAKER_01] stranke udružile.

1227
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:34,340
[SPEAKER_01] Sad vidimo domovijski pokret,

1228
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] nema veze,

1229
00:36:35,420 --> 00:36:36,360
[SPEAKER_01] to je turbo slok,

1230
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:36,599
[SPEAKER_01] suverenizam,

1231
00:36:36,599 --> 00:36:38,380
[SPEAKER_01] nema nikakve veze.

1232
00:36:38,380 --> 00:36:38,920
